### Enable Turbopack Tracing in Next.js Development

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/local-development.mdx

Generates a Turbopack trace file by setting the NEXT_TURBOPACK_TRACING environment variable before running the development server. The trace file captures detailed performance information about module compilation and is saved to the .next/dev folder.

```bash
NEXT_TURBOPACK_TRACING=1 npm run dev
```

