### Interpret Turbopack Trace File with Next.js CLI

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/local-development.mdx

Analyzes the generated trace file using the Next.js internal trace command. This starts a trace server that displays performance metrics through an interactive web-based viewer at https://trace.nextjs.org/.

```bash
npx next internal trace .next/dev/trace-turbopack
```

