### Turbopack Trace Server Command (Legacy)

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/local-development.mdx

Alternative command for older Next.js versions where the trace command was named turbo-trace-server. Provides the same functionality of starting a trace server for visualizing performance data.

```bash
npx next internal turbo-trace-server .next/dev/trace-turbopack
```

