### Run Next.js Development Server with Turbopack or Webpack

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/migrating/from-create-react-app.mdx

Start the Next.js development server, which defaults to Turbopack for faster local development. For compatibility with Create React App's bundler, use the `--webpack` flag to explicitly run the server with Webpack.

```bash
next dev  # Uses Turbopack by default
```

```bash
next dev --webpack
```

