Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/01-getting-started/01-installation.mdx

Defines development lifecycle scripts for Next.js project management. Includes scripts for starting development server with Turbopack, building for production, starting production server, and running ESLint for code quality checks.

