### Install @next/bundle-analyzer plugin

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/package-bundling.mdx

Install the Next.js bundle analyzer package using npm, yarn, or pnpm. This plugin generates visual reports showing package sizes and dependencies to help identify optimization opportunities.

```bash
npm i @next/bundle-analyzer
# or
yarn add @next/bundle-analyzer
# or
pnpm add @next/bundle-analyzer
