### Generate bundle analysis report

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/package-bundling.mdx

Run the build process with ANALYZE environment variable set to generate a visual bundle analysis report. The report opens in three browser tabs showing package size breakdowns.

```bash
ANALYZE=true npm run build
# or
ANALYZE=true yarn build
# or
ANALYZE=true pnpm build
```

