### Configure transpilePackages for monorepo bundling

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/package-bundling.mdx

Bundle specific external packages that are not pre-bundled, such as those in a monorepo or imported from node_modules. This option is useful for Pages Router applications.

```javascript
/** @type {import('next').NextConfig} */
const nextConfig = {
  transpilePackages: ['package-name'],
}

module.exports = nextConfig
```
